1.BodyTag Properties
*******************
1.bgcolor(background color) ==> 1.we can give direct color , 2. color code starting with # followed by 6 No's 
2.background ==>To insert image int he background
3.text ===> to give text color (the words present in body will come in this color)

eg:
----
<body bgcolor=#ff5733 background="https://images.pexels.com/photos/248797/pexels-photo-248797.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=350.jpeg"
text="yellow" >

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2.Text Properties
********************
1.Headings
2.General text tags
3.font properties
4.paragraph properties
5.Text reverse

1.Heading
**********
1.align==> left/right/center
2.bold and break are common properties for the headings

<h1 align="center">Welcome</h1>  ===> biggest/larges heading
<h2 align="left">Welcome</h2>
<h3 align="right">Welcome</h3>
<h4>Welcome</h4>
<h5>Welcome</h5>
<h6>Welcome</h6> ====> smallest heading
*********************************************************************
